        <!-- v1 vs v2 delta box -->
        <mxCell id="delta" value="What's new in v2&#xa;&#xa;• L0 Discovery — auto-detect devices (mDNS, HA, plugin manifests)&#xa;• L8 Meta — self-improving loop (observe → evaluate → learn → tune)&#xa;• Embedding-based prompts — 2.5K tokens vs 15–30K in v1&#xa;• Autonomy Slider — per-domain graduated trust (0.0–1.0)&#xa;• Auto-Investigation — active hypothesis testing on anomalies&#xa;• Unified Actuator — goal-based actions across all devices" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF3E0;strokeColor=#E65100;align=left;fontSize=10;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=5" vertex="1" parent="1">
